Description: Creation and selection of N-way Partial Least Squares (NPLS) models. Selection of the optimal number of components can be done using ncrossreg(). NPLS was originally described by Bro 1996 <doi:10.1002/(SICI)1099-128X(199601)10:1<47::AID-CEM400>3.0.CO;2-C>.
